---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Cookie Policy | SESEC"
  description="SESEC's cookie policy. Information about how we use cookies and similar technologies on our website."
  lang="en"
>
  <Section title="Cookie Policy" padding="xl">
    <div class="legal-content">
      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>1. What are Cookies?</h3>
        <p>Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and provide information to website owners.</p>
        
        <p>Cookies can be "persistent" (remain on your device until deleted or expired) or "session" (deleted when you close your browser).</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>2. Types of Cookies We Use</h3>
        
        <h4>2.1 Essential Cookies</h4>
        <p>These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly:</p>
        
        <div class="cookie-table">
          <div class="cookie-row">
            <div class="cookie-name"><strong>Session ID</strong></div>
            <div class="cookie-purpose">Maintains user session state</div>
            <div class="cookie-duration">Session</div>
          </div>
          <div class="cookie-row">
            <div class="cookie-name"><strong>Language Preference</strong></div>
            <div class="cookie-purpose">Remembers selected language</div>
            <div class="cookie-duration">1 year</div>
          </div>
          <div class="cookie-row">
            <div class="cookie-name"><strong>Cookie Consent</strong></div>
            <div class="cookie-purpose">Stores cookie preferences</div>
            <div class="cookie-duration">1 year</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h4>2.2 Performance Cookies</h4>
        <p>These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website:</p>
        
        <div class="cookie-table">
          <div class="cookie-row">
            <div class="cookie-name"><strong>Analytics</strong></div>
            <div class="cookie-purpose">Collects anonymous usage statistics</div>
            <div class="cookie-duration">2 years</div>
          </div>
          <div class="cookie-row">
            <div class="cookie-name"><strong>Page Views</strong></div>
            <div class="cookie-purpose">Tracks page popularity</div>
            <div class="cookie-duration">30 days</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h4>2.3 Functionality Cookies</h4>
        <p>These cookies enhance your experience by remembering your preferences:</p>
        
        <div class="cookie-table">
          <div class="cookie-row">
            <div class="cookie-name"><strong>Theme Preference</strong></div>
            <div class="cookie-purpose">Remembers dark/light mode choice</div>
            <div class="cookie-duration">1 year</div>
          </div>
          <div class="cookie-row">
            <div class="cookie-name"><strong>Form Data</strong></div>
            <div class="cookie-purpose">Saves partially completed forms</div>
            <div class="cookie-duration">7 days</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>3. Purpose of Cookie Use</h3>
        
        <h4>3.1 Website Functionality</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Enable core website features</li>
          <li>Remember user preferences</li>
          <li>Maintain session state</li>
          <li>Provide personalized experience</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>3.2 Performance Analysis</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Understand user behavior patterns</li>
          <li>Identify popular content</li>
          <li>Optimize website performance</li>
          <li>Improve user experience</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>3.3 Security</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Prevent fraudulent activity</li>
          <li>Protect against spam</li>
          <li>Secure user sessions</li>
          <li>Detect suspicious behavior</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>4. Legal Basis</h3>
        <p>Our use of cookies is based on:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Consent:</strong> For non-essential cookies (performance, functionality)</li>
          <li><strong>Legitimate Interest:</strong> For essential cookies required for website operation</li>
          <li><strong>Legal Obligation:</strong> For cookies required by applicable laws</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>5. Managing Cookies</h3>
        
        <h4>5.1 Cookie Preference Center</h4>
        <p>You can manage your cookie preferences through our cookie banner that appears on your first visit. You can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Accept all cookies</li>
          <li>Reject non-essential cookies</li>
          <li>Customize preferences by category</li>
          <li>Change preferences at any time</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>5.2 Browser Settings</h4>
        <p>You can also control cookies through your browser settings:</p>
        
        <div class="browser-instructions">
          <h5>Chrome:</h5>
          <p>Settings → Privacy and Security → Cookies and other site data</p>
          
          <h5>Firefox:</h5>
          <p>Options → Privacy & Security → Cookies and Site Data</p>
          
          <h5>Safari:</h5>
          <p>Preferences → Privacy → Manage Website Data</p>
          
          <h5>Edge:</h5>
          <p>Settings → Cookies and site permissions → Cookies and site data</p>
        </div>
        
        <h4>5.3 Third-Party Tools</h4>
        <p>You can use third-party tools to manage cookies:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Browser extensions for cookie management</li>
          <li>Privacy-focused browsers</li>
          <li>Ad blockers with cookie controls</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>6. Consequences of Disabling Cookies</h3>
        
        <h4>6.1 Essential Cookies</h4>
        <p>Disabling essential cookies may result in:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Website functionality issues</li>
          <li>Inability to maintain sessions</li>
          <li>Loss of user preferences</li>
          <li>Security vulnerabilities</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>6.2 Non-Essential Cookies</h4>
        <p>Disabling non-essential cookies may result in:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Less personalized experience</li>
          <li>Repeated cookie consent requests</li>
          <li>Limited analytics insights</li>
          <li>Reduced website optimization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>7. Third-Party Cookies</h3>
        
        <h4>7.1 Analytics Services</h4>
        <p>We may use third-party analytics services that set their own cookies:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Website usage analytics</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy Policy:</strong> <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out</a></li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>7.2 Content Delivery</h4>
        <p>We use content delivery networks that may set cookies:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Font loading services</li>
          <li>Image optimization services</li>
          <li>Security services</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>8. Data Retention</h3>
        <p>Cookie data is retained for the following periods:</p>
        
        <div class="retention-table">
          <div class="retention-row">
            <div class="retention-type"><strong>Session Cookies</strong></div>
            <div class="retention-period">Until browser is closed</div>
          </div>
          <div class="retention-row">
            <div class="retention-type"><strong>Persistent Cookies</strong></div>
            <div class="retention-period">As specified in cookie settings (max 2 years)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="retention-row">
            <div class="retention-type"><strong>Analytics Data</strong></div>
            <div class="retention-period">26 months maximum</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>9. Updates to This Policy</h3>
        <p>We may update this cookie policy periodically to reflect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Changes in cookie usage</li>
          <li>New legal requirements</li>
          <li>Technology updates</li>
          <li>Service improvements</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Updates will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>10. Contact Information</h3>
        <p>For questions about our cookie policy:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@sesecpro.com">privacy@sesecpro.com</a></li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +34 XXX XXX XXX</li>
          <li><strong>Address:</strong> Spain</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2025</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .legal-section h3 {
    color: var(--fg);
    font-size: var(--fs-h3);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .legal-section h4 {
    color: var(--fg);
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-2) 0;
  }
  
  .legal-section h5 {
    color: var(--fg);
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-1) 0;
  }
  
  .legal-section p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  
  .legal-section ul {
    margin: var(--space-3) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--dur) var(--ease);
  }
  
  .legal-section a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-2);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  /* Cookie Tables */
  .cookie-table, .retention-table {
    background: var(--glass);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin: var(--space-4) 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .cookie-row, .retention-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr 1fr;
    padding: var(--space-3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }
  
  .retention-row {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }
  
  .cookie-row:last-child, .retention-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  
  .cookie-name, .retention-type {
    color: var(--fg);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .cookie-purpose {
    color: var(--fg-dim);
  }
  
  .cookie-duration, .retention-period {
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
  }
  
  /* Browser Instructions */
  .browser-instructions {
    background: var(--glass);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    margin: var(--space-4) 0;
  }
  
  .browser-instructions h5 {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .browser-instructions h5:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  
  .browser-instructions p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    background: var(--bg-2);
    padding: var(--space-2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-content {
      padding: 0 var(--space-4);
    }
    
    .legal-section h3 {
      font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    }
    
    .cookie-row, .retention-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }
    
    .browser-instructions {
      padding: var(--space-4);
    }
  }
</style>